texts.text: Library is an Education Edition feature to simplify the process of finding and importing educational content directly in the game.

The buildings in villages that contain bookshelves and lecterns.
The rooms in strongholds that contain bookshelves and chests.
The rooms in woodland mansions that contain bookshelves.
The enchanting library, a player-built structure to increase enchanting table power.
